title: Lovely 3BR, 2BA House w/ 2-car GA Near Como
posting_body: ['Available for SEPT.', '15th move-in.', 'Six month or 12-month lease available.', 'Looking for CONSCIENTIOUS renters who will respect the property.', 'NO pets, NO smoking.', 'Renter will be provided with a lawnmower and snow blower to use and RENTER is responsible for SNOW REMOVAL and MOWING the lawn in a timely manner.', "**We are currently repainting and fixing up the property (refinishing the hardwood floors), so house won't be ready for showings until the last weeks of August.", 'Rent: $1750/month', 'Damage Deposit: $1200 (refundable if the home is kept in excellent condition)', 'Renters pay: All utilities except trash', 'Application fee: $30 (Application required for each adult who will be living in the property)', 'Lovely home built in the early 1900s, but with some nice updates like central air, refinished hardwood floors, gas range and dishwasher.', 'Three bedrooms upstairs and a full bath.', 'Two of the bedrooms have double closets, and the smallest BR walks out to a small balcony overlooking the backyard and pear and apple trees.', 'Main level has a half bath, full kitchen, living room, large dining room, front foyer, three-season front porch and a back entryway.', 'Basement is mainly a storage and laundry area, but a large family room area has been created as well with a cozy electric fireplace.', 'For more information, or to apply, please call LaDawn at', 'show contact info', '.', 'We are NOT set up for Section 8, sorry!']
